import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { Grid, Button, TextField } from '@mui/material';

const DialPad = () => {
    const [number, setNumber] = useState('');

    const handleNumberChange = (event) => {
        setNumber(event.target.value);
    };

    const handleCallClick = () => {
        console.log(`Calling number: ${number}`);
        // Add your logic for initiating a call here
    };

    const handleDeleteClick = () => {
        setNumber(number.slice(0, -1));
    };

    return (
        <Grid container spacing={2} justify="center">
            <Grid item xs={12}>
                <TextField
                    label="הזן מספר טלפון"
                    value={number}
                    onChange={handleNumberChange}
                    variant="standard"
                    fullWidth
                />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}1`)}>
                    1
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}2`)}>
                    2
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}3`)}>
                    3
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}4`)}>
                    4
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}5`)}>
                    5
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}6`)}>
                    6
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}7`)}>
                    7
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}8`)}>
                    8
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}9`)}>
                    9
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}*`)}>
                    *
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}0`)}>
                    0
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={4}>
                <Button variant="outlined" onClick={() => setNumber(`${number}#`)}>
                    #
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
                <Button fullWidth variant="outlined" onClick={handleDeleteClick}>
                    מחק
                </Button>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12}>
                <Button
                    variant="contained"
                    color="primary"
                    onClick={handleCallClick}
                    fullWidth
                >
                    חייג
                </Button>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    );
};

export default DialPad;
